Build instructions:

First build and install Apache2 with mod_ssl enabled.

To compile the module:
/path/to/apache2/bin/apxs -lssl -lcrypto -I/path/to/ssl/include -L/path/to/ssl/lib -c mod_dtcpip_auth.c s_dtcp_interface.c

To install and activate the module:
sudo /path/to/apache2/bin/apxs -i -a mod_dtcpip_auth.la

Available module flags:

DTCPLibraryPath /absolute/path/to/dtcp_library.so
DTCPKeyStorageDir /absolute/path/to/key_storage_dir
# on/off values are case sensitive
DTCPRequireReneg on
DTCPSendCerts on
DTCPEnableDTCPEncryption on
DTCPEncryptionPort portnum
